47 template<unsigned int spacedim>
48 class OmegaFluxDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
49 {
50 
51 private:
52 
56  const double D;
57 
58 public:
59 
77  OmegaFluxDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
78  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
79  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
80  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
81  const double D,
82  const unsigned int method,
83  const double alpha = 0.0)
84  :
85  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 0, 1, method, alpha, "OmegaFluxDissipation00"),
86  D(D)
87  {
88  }
89 
93  bool
94  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
95  const double /*t*/,
96  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
97  double& omega,
98  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
99  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
100  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
101  const bool compute_dq)
102  const
103  {
104  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> i;
105  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
106  i[m] = values[m];
107  const double q = values[3] > 1e-16 ? values[3] : 1e-16;
108 
109  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
110  {
111  omega = 1.0 / ( 2.0 * D * q) * i * i;
112  }
113 
114  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
115  {
116  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
117  d_omega[m] = 1.0 / ( D * q ) * i[m];
118  }
119 
120  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
121  {
122  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
123  d2_omega(m, m) = 1.0 / ( D * q );
124 
125  if(compute_dq && (q > 1e-16))
126  {
127  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
128  d2_omega(m, 3) = - 1.0 / ( D * q * q ) * i[m];
129  }
130  }
131 
132  return false;
133  }

184  OmegaDualFluxDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
185  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
186  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
187  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
188  const double D,
189  const unsigned int method,
190  const double alpha = 0.0)
191  :
192  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 3, 1, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluxDissipation00"),
193  D(D)
194  {
195  }
196 
200  bool
201  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
202  const double /*t*/,
203  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
204  double& omega,
205  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
206  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
207  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
208  const bool compute_dq)
209  const
210  {
211  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> E;
212  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
213  E[m] = values[m];
214  const double q = values[3];
215 
216  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
217  {
218  omega = -D * q / 2.0 * E * E;
219  }
220 
221  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
222  {
223  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
224  d_omega[m] = -D * q * E[m];
225  }
226 
227  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
228  {
229  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
230  d2_omega(m, m) = -D * q;
231 
232  if(compute_dq)
233  {
234  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
235  d2_omega(m, 3) = -D * E[m];
236  }
237  }
238 
239 
240  return false;
241  }

906 template<unsigned int spacedim>

952  bool
953  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,

956  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
957  double& sigma,
958  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
959  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
960  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
961  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
962  const
963  {
964 
965  const double I_x_dot = values[0];
966  const double I_y_dot = values[1];

968  const double n_x = n[0];

971 
972  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))

974  sigma = 1.0/(2.0*D) * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
975  }
976 
977  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
978  {
979  d_sigma[0] = 1.0/D * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * n_x;
980  d_sigma[1] = 1.0/D * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * n_y;
981  d_sigma[2] = 1.0/D * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * n_z;
982  }
983

1106  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1107  {
1108  t1 = exp(beta * threshold);
1109  t2 = exp( (beta - 1.0) * threshold);
1110  }
1111  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1112  {
1113  t1 = exp(-beta * threshold);
1114  t2 = exp( -(beta - 1.0) * threshold);
1115  }
1116  else

1119  t2 = exp( (beta - 1.0) * eta / RT);
1120  }

1123  {
1124  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1125  sigma = t1 / beta + t2 / (1.0 - beta) + (t1 - t2) * (eta / RT - threshold) + 0.5 * (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT - threshold) * (eta / RT - threshold);
1126  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1127  sigma = t1 / beta + t2 / (1.0 - beta) + (t1 - t2) * (eta / RT + threshold) + 0.5 * (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT + threshold) * (eta / RT + threshold);
1128  else
1129  sigma = t1/beta + t2/(1.0 - beta);
1130  sigma *= -I_0;
1131  }
1132 
1133  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1134  {
1135  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1136  {
1137  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2) + (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT - threshold);
1138  }
1139  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1140  {
1141  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2) + (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT + threshold);
1142  }
1143  else
1144  {
1145  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2);
1146  }
1147  d_sigma[0] *= -I_0 / RT;
1148  }
1149 
1150  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1151  {
1152  if(eta / RT > threshold)

1155  }
1156  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1157  {
1158  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1159  }
1160  else
1161  {
1162  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1163  }

3272  const double t,

3274  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
3275  double& sigma,
3276  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
3277  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
3278  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
3279  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
3280  const
3281  {
3282 
3283  const double time_old = phi_bar.get_time();
3284  phi_bar.set_time(t);
3285  const double eta_bar_ = -A_e * F * phi_bar.value(x);
3286  phi_bar.set_time(time_old);
3287 
3288  const double eta_int = values[0];
3289  const double delta_eta = eta_int + eta_bar_;
3290 
3291  // iterate for corresponding current
3292  double I_k = 0.0;
3293  double f_old = 1e16;
3294  unsigned int iter = 0;
3295  for(;;)
3296  {
3297  iter++;
3298  const double f = asinh(I_k * F / i_0) + 1.0 / RT * R_el * F * F * I_k + delta_eta / RT;
3299  if(fabs(fabs(f) - fabs(f_old)) < 1e-16)
3300  break;
3301  if(iter == 100)
3302  return true;
3303  f_old = f;
3304  const double df_dI_k = (F / i_0) / sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) + 1.0 / RT * R_el * F * F;
3305  const double dI_k = - f / df_dI_k;
3306  I_k = I_k + dI_k;
3307  }
3308 
3309  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3310  sigma = delta_eta * I_k - i_0 * RT / F * ( sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) - 1.0 ) + RT * I_k * asinh(I_k * F / i_0) + 0.5 * R_el * (I_k * F) * (I_k * F);
3311

3314

3318  }
3319 
3320  return false;
3321  }

3545  return false;

4741  const bool compute_dq)

4744 
4745  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot, v_dot, u_dot_v_dot, t;
4746  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
4747 
4748 
4749  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4750  {
4751  u_dot[r] = values[r];
4752  v_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
4753  t[r] = values[6 + r];
4754  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4755  F[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
4756  }
4757  F_inv = invert(F);
4758  u_dot_v_dot = u_dot - v_dot;
4759  const double J = determinant(F);
4760 
4761  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
4762  n__[0] = n[0];
4763  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
4764  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
4765  n_ = J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
4766 
4767  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4768  {
4769  sigma = t * cross_product_3d(u_dot_v_dot, n_) + 0.5 * (t * n_) * (t * n_);
4770  }
4771 
4772  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4773  {
4774  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4775  {
4776  d_sigma[r] = cross_product_3d(n_, t)[r];
4777  d_sigma[3 + r] = -cross_product_3d(n_, t)[r];
4778  d_sigma[6 + r] = cross_product_3d(u_dot_v_dot, n_)[r] + (t * n_) * n_[r];
4779  }
4780  }
4781 
4782  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4783  {
4784  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 0) = 0.0;
4785  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 1) = -n_[2];
4786  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 2) = n_[1];
4787  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 0) = n_[2];
4788  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 1) = 0.0;
4789  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 2) = -n_[0];
4790  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 0) = -n_[1];
4791  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 1) = n_[0];
4792  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 2) = 0.0;
4793 
4794  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 0) = 0.0;
4795  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 1) = n_[2];
4796  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 2) = -n_[1];
4797  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 0) = -n_[2];
4798  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 1) = 0.0;
4799  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 2) = n_[0];
4800  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 0) = n_[1];
4801  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 1) = -n_[0];
4802  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 2) = 0.0;
4803 
4804  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
4805  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
4806  d2_sigma(6 + m, 6 + l) = n_[m] * n_[l];
4807 
4808  if(compute_dq)
4809  {
4810  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
4811  dealii::Tensor<2,3> t_dn_dF;
4812  const double t_n = t * n_;
4813  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
4814  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4815  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4816  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
4817  t_dn_dF = t * dn_dF;
4818  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4819  {
4820  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4821  {
4822  d2_sigma(0, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[2] - dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[1];
4823  d2_sigma(1, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[0] - dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[2];
4824  d2_sigma(2, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[1] - dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[0];
4825  d2_sigma(3, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[2] + dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[1];
4826  d2_sigma(4, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[0] + dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[2];
4827  d2_sigma(5, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[1] + dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[0];
4828  d2_sigma(6, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[1][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[2] + dn_dF[2][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[1] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[0] + t_n * dn_dF[0][r][R];
4829  d2_sigma(7, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[2][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[0] + dn_dF[0][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[2] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[1] + t_n * dn_dF[1][r][R];
4830  d2_sigma(8, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[0][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[1] + dn_dF[1][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[0] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[2] + t_n * dn_dF[2][r][R];
4831  }
4832  }
4833  }
4834  }
4835 
4836  return false;
4837  }
